description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to the Tampa Bay Times' Rick Stroud about Brady's return. Is it more surprising that he's returning or that he ever retired to begin with? The MMQB's Albert Breer explains why the Browns shouldn't be ruled out in making a run at Deshaun Watson. And Seth Greenberg tells us which potential Cinderella teams to look out for
